projects.name: Build a Browser Code Editor in React
projects.description: Developed a browser-based code editor using React, enabling a responsive and interactive coding environment. Integrated support for multiple programming languages, including Python and Java, within the editor interface. Implemented code execution and output/error display features, allowing users to run code and view results directly in the browser.

projects.name: Weather API Integration
projects.description: Integrated a Weather API using JavaScript to fetch real-time weather data for various locations. Developed a user interface with HTML and CSS to display current weather conditions, forecasts, and other relevant information. Implemented JavaScript for error handling and data validation, ensuring accurate and reliable weather information is presented to users.

projects.name: ChatEase: Realtime Private Chat Application
projects.description: Developed a responsive chat interface using React, providing a seamless experience for private, real-time messaging with components for user interaction and chat management. Utilized Firebase for backend support, including Firestore for real-time data synchronization, Firebase Authentication for secure user logins, and Cloud Functions for serverless operations. Implemented secure and instant messaging with end-to-end encryption, ensuring private conversations and reliable message delivery.
